                Upon successful registration you will be automatically loggen into the site
            </p>
            <img style="border:solid; border-color:black;" src="~/Images/FAQs/Loggedin.PNG" alt="Quick Register step 03" />
            <br /><br />
        </div>

        <br /><br />
        <h4>1.2 Register(Full Register)</h4>
        <p>
            Just like any other registration process our <strong>Full Register</strong> requires basic information about you. Lets get started with <strong>Full Register</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>Start by Locating and clicking on <strong>Register</strong> link on your top right corner which will direct you to our registration page</li>
                <li>Please provide the basic information required by this page <strong style="color:red"> Please note that all fields are required</strong></li>
                <li style="color:red">Please note that the password has to be at least 6 characters long, and your email not been previously registerd</li>
                <li>Upon providing the required information find and click the <strong>Register</strong> button on the bottom left of the page </li>
